without noticing that his staff isn't here.

12:05.850 --> 12:07.643
Text me when you're done
with your parents tonight.

12:12.273 --> 12:14.983
Where's... Where is everybody?

12:16.194 --> 12:17.361
Welcome back, man.

12:17.570 --> 12:20.072
