12:41.052 --> 12:42.719
Okay. Ooh!

12:43.346 --> 12:44.930
Couldn't say the answer from over there?

12:45.014 --> 12:46.348
- Welcome back.
- Thank you.

12:46.433 --> 12:48.058
Charlie Skinner needs to see you in his office.

12:48.184 --> 12:49.852
- Now?
- He said as soon as you come in.

12:49.936 --> 12:51.353
What's... You're Ellen?

12:51.438 --> 12:53.147
- Maggie, Margaret.
- What's going on?

12:53.231 --> 12:54.898
We know as little as you do.

12:54.983 --> 12:56.442
- Really?
- Almost as little as you do.

12:56.526 --> 12:57.901
What's the part that you know that I don't?

12:57.986 --> 12:59.903
- You should talk to Charlie Skinner.
- Where's Karen?

13:00.363 --> 13:02.489
- There's no one who works here named Karen.
- My assistant.

13:02.574 --> 13:04.700
- I'm your assistant.
- You're Ellen.

13:05.076 --> 13:06.702
- Margaret.
- Okay.

13:07.078 --> 13:09.204
Uh, I'll let his secretary know
you're on your way.

13:09.289 --> 13:10.581
Her name is Karen.

13:10.999 --> 13:12.958
No one's named Karen. No one.

13:13.042 --> 13:14.793
- All right.
- I'll call up for you.

13:19.549 --> 13:21.800
Angela, hi. It's Maggie from downstairs.

13:22.302 --> 13:23.844
- You can go on in. He's waiting for you.
- Thank you.

13:23.928 --> 13:25.971
You own this now,
my friend. You have bought it.

13:26.055 --> 13:29.266
You have paid for it and you have the receipt.
I wanna be crystal clear, this is yours.

13:29.350 --> 13:30.434
You're wearing it.

13:30.518 --> 13:32.227
- Henry wants me to make sure you know that.
- Wait.

13:32.312 --> 13:33.979
Mr. Will McAvoy has just
stepped into my office,

13:34.063 --> 13:35.898
so I need to walk him through this.

13:35.982 --> 13:37.691
- Shit, how much does he know?
- You're on speaker.

13:37.775 --> 13:38.984
I don't know anything. Who is this?

13:39.068 --> 13:41.153
Heh-hey, Will! How was the vaca...

