13:44.115 --> 13:45.365
I don't know what just happened there.

13:45.450 --> 13:48.744
Two weeks in Saint Lucia
was just what the doctor ordered, literally.

13:49.579 --> 13:50.996
- You've got pictures?
- No.

13:51.080 --> 13:52.664
Don't worry about it. TMZ does.

13:52.749 --> 13:55.083
