the woman spun twice,

14:28.409 --> 14:30.911
teetered over, and fell right into my lap.

14:30.995 --> 14:34.289
That was a story about how sometimes
things fall right into your lap.

14:35.875 --> 14:36.959
Where's my staff?

14:37.043 --> 14:39.753
